===Etymology===
An irregular romanization of {{etyl|zh|en}} {{m|zh|陝西||[Land] [[west|West]] of the [[Shan]] [[pass|Pass]]|tr=Shǎnxī}}, with the first syllable from the [[Gwoyeu Romatzyh]] system and the second from [[pinyin]], in order to distinguish it from the province of {{m|zh|山西||[Land] [[west|West]] of the [Taihang] [[mountain|Mountains]]|tr=Shānxī}} in atonal spelling. When tone marks are present, the single-A ''[[Shǎnxī]]'' is the correct form.

